text: One of the seemingly more realistic situations I have playing out in my head right now is that as AI starts taking jobs (Artists, Programmers) certain industries manage to successfully lobby the government to make AI illegal to use in their field. Doctors and Lawyers seem like a good bet for jobs that politicians will arbitrarily keep safe.
